---
// FAQ Section
---

<section class="faq-section" id="faq" data-fade-in>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-container">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Why is Mellon free?</summary>
        <p>We believe everyone deserves access to fast, private voice-to-text. Mellon runs entirely on your Mac. No cloud, no subscriptions, no data collection. We're building tools we want to exist in the world, and making them free is part of that vision.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How can I support or donate?</summary>
        <p>If Mellon has been useful to you, we'd love your support! You can donate via our website. Every contribution helps us pay maintainence costs and improving Mellon and adding new features. It's completely optional and never required.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Which macOS versions are supported?</summary>
        <p>Mellon works on macOS 12 (Monterey) and newer. We recommend running the latest macOS version for the best experience.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How is this different from built-in macOS dictation?</summary>
        <p>Mellon offers faster processing, better accuracy, custom shortcuts, and works universally across all apps. Plus, everything stays completely local with no Apple cloud processing.</p>
      </details>

  
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ========== FAQ SECTION ========== */
  .faq-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: var(--space-3xl) auto 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: 16px;
    outline: none;
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::before {
    content: 'â–¶';
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: var(--space-sm);
    transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::before {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>

